## Musts

- **PHI → OpenAI** only if BAA signed; otherwise pass **de-identified** text (Safe Harbor: remove 18 identifiers) and track provenance.
- Prefer **Comprehend Medical** for entity extraction when PHI present (HIPAA-eligible); Whisper/Polly usage must follow HIPAA-eligible service policies.
- **Cost controls**: rate limit and batch for embeddings; cache deterministic prompts; measure tokens per feature.

## Don’t

- Don’t store raw prompts/responses with PHI; store identifiers + encrypted payloads only when required.
